03:07.720 --> 03:11.664
You told me you had something interesting to say about the How We Die book.

03:11.724 --> 03:12.705
Oh, yeah.

03:12.905 --> 03:14.827
Well, it's probably, it can't be on the record.

03:14.987 --> 03:16.148
Okay.

03:16.549 --> 03:17.910
Off the record.

03:18.130 --> 03:18.371
Yeah.

03:18.671 --> 03:19.632
Just push the button.

03:22.227 --> 03:23.448
Okay.

