Yeah, 89.3.

12:14.519 --> 12:15.521
89.3.

12:15.601 --> 12:17.203
Actually, let's keep going.

12:17.343 --> 12:17.804
Yeah.

12:17.824 --> 12:18.585
Let's go for it.

12:18.625 --> 12:19.746
Let's shatter the record.

12:19.966 --> 12:21.969
I've never seen so much snow here.

12:21.989 --> 12:23.892
I really thought that was an invented language.

12:23.952 --> 12:27.416
Now, this actually, I don't want to give anything away in my piece.

12:27.436 --> 12:27.797
Right.

12:28.277 --> 12:29.239
Yeah, it's actually Hungarian.

12:30.520 --> 12:32.343
