Do me a favor.

12:55.674 --> 12:56.175
Don't put that in.

12:56.195 --> 12:56.716
I won't.

12:56.976 --> 13:02.823
I just, I actually thought that they were in, but you really, I'm very good at this.

13:03.564 --> 13:04.705
